json-schema-validator
------------------------------------------
This is a C++ library for validating JSON documents based on a JSON Schema
which itself should validate with draft-7 of JSON Schema Validation.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.5.4-1
  libgcc1-12.4.0-3
  libnlohmann_json_schema_validator-devel-2.3.0-1bl1
  libnlohmann_json_schema_validator2-2.3.0-1bl1
  libstdc++6-12.4.0-3
  pkg-config-2.3.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.43.1-1
  cmake-3.28.3-1
  cygport-0.36.9-1
  gcc-core-12.4.0-3
  gcc-g++-12.4.0-3
  make-4.4.1-2
  ninja-1.12.0-1
  nlohmann_json-3.11.3-1bl1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/pboettch/json-schema-validator

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/pboettch/json-schema-validator/archive/refs/tags/2.3.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack json-schema-validator-2.3.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./json-schema-validator-2.3.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/json-schema-validator-2.3.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/json-schema-validator-2.3.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libnlohmann_json_schema_validator2-2.3.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libnlohmann_json_schema_validator-devel-2.3.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(json-schema-validator)
  /usr/bin/format-json-schema.exe
  /usr/bin/json-schema-validate.exe
  /usr/bin/readme-json-schema.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/json-schema-validator.README
  /usr/share/doc/json-schema-validator/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/json-schema-validator/README.md

(libnlohmann_json_schema_validator2)
  /usr/bin/cygnlohmann_json_schema_validator-2.dll

(libnlohmann_json_schema_validator-devel)
  /usr/include/nlohmann/json-schema.hpp
  /usr/lib/cmake/nlohmann_json_schema_validator/nlohmann_json_schema_validatorConfig.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/nlohmann_json_schema_validator/nlohmann_json_schema_validatorConfigVersion.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/nlohmann_json_schema_validator/nlohmann_json_schema_validatorTargets-release.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/nlohmann_json_schema_validator/nlohmann_json_schema_validatorTargets.cmake
  /usr/lib/libnlohmann_json_schema_validator.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/json-schema-validator.pc

